<div class="artist-statement">
  <div class="about-me">
    <h2 class="main-subtitle"> About me</h2>
      <br>
      <p class="main-text">I started painting at a moment in my life where I needed to channel strong emotions.</p>
      <br>
      <p class="main-text">I grew up in Africa and Spain and this has inspired my work in particular my understanding of colour, light and the passion in my themes. Vibrant colour, music and people's feelings, in particular love, are a constant thread in my work. While leading a successful career in business, art has always been a source of peace, and a way to express emotion and creativity beyond what my day to day allows.</p>
      <br>

      <p class="main-text">I paint at home (in London) and every painting is a reflection of a particular emotion inspired by a dream, a scene observed in her commute, a song, an episode of my life, etc...</p>
  </div>

